<div class="gecko-accordions">
  {%- assign accordion_uid = section.id | default: 'gecko' -%}
  <div class="product__accordion accordion quick-add-hidden">
      <details id="Details-gecko-details-{{ accordion_uid }}">
      <summary>
        <div class="summary__title">
          <h2 class="h4 accordion__title inline-richtext">Item details</h2>
        </div>
        {{- 'icon-caret.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
      </summary>
      <div class="accordion__content rte">
        <p>Capture your furry friend's unique personality in a vibrant, custom photo tropical style <strong>cat Hawaii Shirt</strong>! Perfect for the cat lover in your life, it also makes a memorable summer or beach trip gift!</p>
        <p><strong>Preview:</strong><br>- Choose an option and upload your photo.<br>- Click <strong>Preview Your Personalization</strong> to see the preview.<br>- Double-check your options before purchasing.</p>
        <p><strong>Product Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fabric: 100% polyester</li>
          <li>Regular fit</li>
          <li>Short sleeve, lapel collar, button closure</li>
          <li>Fabric weight: 120g/m²</li>
          <li>Care: machine wash cold, do not bleach, tumble dry low</li>
          <li>Made on demand — no minimum order quantity</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> 3–5 business days<br><strong>Shipping Time:</strong> 10–15 business days</p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
  <div class="product__accordion accordion quick-add-hidden">
    <details id="Details-gecko-shipping-{{ accordion_uid }}">
      <summary>
        <div class="summary__title">
          <h2 class="h4 accordion__title inline-richtext">Shipping Info</h2>
        </div>
        {{- 'icon-caret.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
      </summary>
      <div class="accordion__content rte">
        <ul>
          <li>The above time frame is only applied for orders to the US with standard shipping methods.</li>
          <li>International orders: It may take 2–5 days longer due to the customs clearance process.</li>
          <li><strong>Orders can be cancelled or modified only within 2 hours after being placed.</strong></li>
          <li>All products are made to order.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
  <div class="product__accordion accordion quick-add-hidden">
    <details id="Details-gecko-guarantee-{{ accordion_uid }}">
      <summary>
        <div class="summary__title">
          <h2 class="h4 accordion__title inline-richtext">Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>
        </div>
        {{- 'icon-caret.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
      </summary>
      <div class="accordion__content rte">
        <ul>
          <li>Full-refund or replace a new item (no extra fee within 30 days since your purchase) for faulty, defective or damaged products.</li>
          <li>Full-refund if the item is not as described.</li>
          <li>We have 24/7/365 ticket and email support.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
  <div class="product__accordion accordion quick-add-hidden">
    <details id="Details-gecko-deals-{{ accordion_uid }}">
      <summary>
        <div class="summary__title">
          <h2 class="h4 accordion__title inline-richtext">Hot Deals</h2>
        </div>
        {{- 'icon-caret.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
      </summary>
      <div class="accordion__content rte">
        <p>Get ready for a shopping experience like no other! Explore our latest collection tailored for dog and cat lovers, camping enthusiasts, and families alike.</p>
        <p><strong>Enjoy an exclusive 10% discount using code HOT10, combinable with other codes.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
